## Signature phrasing (keep; don’t overuse)

These are “btn0s tells” — use sparingly so they stay sharp.

- “This sounds simple. It is not.”
- “Get it wrong, and …”
- “Not X. Y.”
- “Build something that lets someone else begin.”
- “The invisible infrastructure…”

